                    <WebAddress>https://www.ntsb.gov/investigations/Pages/All-Investigations.aspx</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Investigations</Header>
                <Paragraph>The NTSB maintains a database of major aviation, highway, marine, pipeline, and railroad investigations, both ongoing and completed, on its website.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
